[h3 
	" Knuckles in Sonic The Hedgehog TAS by JXQ
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	[b 
		"Essentials:
	]b
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"This run satisfies the following criteria:
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" Aims for fastest time
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Takes damage to save time
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Abuses programming errors
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Ignores delays caused by bonus effects
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[ul 
	[li 
		" Emulator used: Gens 9Z
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[ul 
	[li 
		" Suggested Screenshot:
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	[img class=embed src=http://img146.imageshack.us/img146/518/sonic1k3fj4.png 
	]img
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Here we have an impressive hack put together by Stealth, placing Knuckles into Sonic the Hedgehog 1.  The game has been discussed here a bit, but you can find its official topic 
	[a class=extlink href=http://info.sonicretro.org/Knuckles_the_Echidna_in_Sonic_the_Hedgehog rel=nofollow 
		"here
	]a
	" at the Sonic 2 Beta message board.  All of Knuckles' abilities are preserved and are true to the feel of playing as Knuckles in other Sonic games with LOCK-ON TECHNOLOGY.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"I worked on this run and my 
	[a class=intlink href=/1383S 
		"Sonic run
	]a
	" concurrently.  The games were similar enough that doing them together helped keeped things fresh in my mind, yet different enough that it didn't get too repetitive.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"I suggest watching the Sonic run first before this one, because the Sonic run shows how the game was meant to be played before watching this run break that mold.
	$LF
]p
